# ADK Synapser

Skill: `.cursor/skills/livskompassen-synapser-adk/SKILL.md`  
Runtime: `functions/src/adk/synapses/synapseBus.ts`, `stateStore.ts`, `orchestrator.ts` (`gatekeeperSanitize`)

## Triggers

| Trigger | Handler | Status | Effekt |
|---------|---------|--------|--------|
| `drive_file_ingested` | `driveIngestSynapse` | **live** (G10) | `classifyInboxDocument` (DCAP-first) → `kb_docs` \| `reality_vault` \| `children_logs` \| `inbox_queue` |
| `user_overwhelm` | `paralysBrytarenSynapse` | **live** | Ett mikrosteg, max 30s |
| `journal_woven` | `journalWovenSynapse` | **live** (G7) | Opt-in `optIn===true` → `kampspar` + vector |
| `dcap_alert` | `dcapAlertSynapse` | **live** | HITL → `dcap_alerts` WORM vid risk ≥70 |
| `widget_recording_ingested` | `widgetRecordingIngestSynapse` | **live** (G10 våg 3) | WH1 commit → `classifyInboxDocument` → `routeInboxToWorm` (block kunskap) |

Koppling: `notifyNewFile` → `emitSynapse(..., drive_file_ingested)` · `ingestWidgetRecording` → `emitSynapse(..., widget_recording_ingested)`.

## Gör alltid

- Kör **DCAP/heuristik före LLM** i `classifyInboxDocument` — routing i kod, inte i prompt.
- Routa bevis till `reality_vault` via `routeInboxToWorm`; routa fakta till `kb_docs`/`kampspar`; barnobservationer till `children_logs`.
- Skicka trauma/LVU utan optIn till `inbox_queue` (HITL) — vänta på manuellt godkännande.
- Hascha payload i synapse state (`hashPayload`) — lagra ingen rå PII.
- Anropa `clearSynapseState` vid utloggning (Zero Footprint).
- Läs prompts från `functions/src/sharedRules.ts` — hårdkoda inte runtime-prompter.

## ADK state ≠ SystemSynapse

`firebase-blueprint.json` definierar Firestore `/synapses/{synapseId}` (`SystemSynapse`).  
ADK använder in-memory `stateStore.ts` — **inte samma** schema (G9). Håll synapse-state isolerat per silo.
